overview:
TrackYourHours is a web-based software developed for Marriage and Family Therapists and Social Workers to easily track and log clinical hours for licensure.

Currently the site allows Trainees and Interns to track hours onÂ a daily or weekly basis, generates the BBS Weekly Summary and Experience Verification forms, provides reporting features to let customers know if ratios are in alignment with BBS regulations and aims to reduce the time and energy surrounding the licensing process.Â  In addition, Track Your Hours hosts an on-line community filled with information and resources to assist pre-licensed clinicians with their path towards licensure.
